By downloading, accessing, or using SwimTrendMapper, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use the app.


### 2. Personal Use Only  
SwimTrendMapper is intended for **personal, non-commercial use only**. You may use the app to track and manage your own swim times or trends. You may not use the app to collect or share data on behalf of others or for commercial purposes.


### 3. User-Generated Content  
Users are responsible for the accuracy and legality of any data they enter into the app. SwimTrendMapper does not verify or moderate user-submitted content.


### 4. Age Restrictions  
SwimTrendMapper is **not intended for users under the age of 13**. If you are under 13, you must use the app only under the supervision of a parent or guardian and through their account. We do not knowingly allow children under 13 to create accounts or submit personal data.


### 5. Compliance with Laws  
You agree to use SwimTrendMapper in compliance with all applicable local, state, national, and international laws and regulations. You may not use the app for any unlawful or prohibited activity.


### 6. Subscription and Payments  
